name: Classico
description:
Hand crafted coffee tamper, in concrete, brass and stainless steel.

Casting concrete creates minor surface holes and the sealer gives a unique patina which develops with age, so no two tampers are the same.

The base is flat bottomed and precision machined from 304 Stainless Steel. Available in 58.35mm (suitable for vst basket) or 58mm diameter (please ensure you measure your machine before ordering).

Designed and made in the UK. 

Free shipping worldwide. Secure payment through paypal or credit / debit card.
